wvb-get-img - take numerical id and db path as parameter, and query sqlite db for img info, write data to stdout in json format
and errors to stderr

wvb-edit-img - take numerical id as parameter, and a json formatted string via stdin to edit img fields

wvb-add-img - receives json formatted string via stdin, img is added to db

wvb-del-img receives numerical id as parameter, deletes img
